spec_data.Name: jchart2d
spec_data.Description:
JChart2D is a minimalist real-time charting library. It is designed for
displaying multiple traces consisting of trace-points. JChart2D is centered
around a single configurable Swing widget: the Chart2D. It is a JComponent
which can be added to a Java Swing user interface.
